  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Cook whole wheat penne according to package instructions until al dente. Drain and set aside.",
    "In a large bowl, mix salmon fillets with figs, raisins, chopped chives, sour cream, dill, garlic powder, and olive oil. Season with salt and pepper if needed.",
    "Transfer the mixture evenly onto prepared whole wheat penne pasta, ensuring each piece is coated.",
    "Bake in preheated oven for 15-20 minutes or until golden brown on top and heated through.",
    "Serve hot as a light lunch dish."
